What  problem we are going to solve in Phase 5

Until now : 
*YOu launch one Ec2
*if it dies -> is down 
*if the traffic increases -> the server become slow or it crashes

Here we are going to understanc how to solve theses  problemsd 


what we are going to do here is : 
    Multiple Ec2 behind a load balancer ,created automatically using the AMI  with the help of the autoscaling 

What we will build here is :

Internet
    |
Application load balancer (ALB)
      |
Auto scaling group (ASG)
       |
EC2 Instances (from your AMI )

